channel.title: What next...I have pics
channel.description:
I can't help it :\ I started trying to make servers about a month ago and failed at it so I want to post pics and see if anyone knows what I did wrong. This will get me back on track. Someone point out what I did wrong. I can already log onto my server though.
By the Way, the 3 digit numbers on starting ip address and the command prompt is my ip address on start>run>cmd>ipconfig. If that isn't the right ip, tell me what I am supposed to use for the portforward starting ip address
